title: 【1.3.2 Seed】 Vast Mountainous Desert With Many NPC Villages & Temples
txt_content:
这种帖子只是看到了就发了- -
Desert Sunrise

One of Many NPC Villages

Sand Temples!

Dividing River

Surface Lava Pool


Seed:
-7899504981172322908World Type:
LargeBiomesSpawn:
X:114, Y:66, Z:-297Features:
A beautiful and vast mountainous Desert Biome stretching over the entire map.
FIVE!  NPC Villages visible within the initial World Map space.
Multiple Sand Temples with some great loot found throughout the Desert Biome.
Small section of Forest Biome located to the Southwest of spawn for wood.
Long River divides the map, there is some visible surface stone areas and an open lava pool.
Credits:
This seed was submitted to Minecraft Seed List from Elias Mendes, thank you
